            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Bertha Goldwasser</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#goldwasserB" start="1836.210" end="x">A Social-Democratic [paper] as it is said, but in reality they are not the way the worker wants to have it.</span>
