            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Bertha Goldwasser</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#goldwasserB" start="1851.948" end="x">There are, but it does not have too much of a success [following] I am not talking now as a follower of the Neue Presse . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
